      <title>OpenAI 首席运营官表示，现在看到人工智能对经济的全面影响还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-10/openai-coo-says-it-s-too-soon-to-see-ai-s-full-impact-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生成式人工智能的兴起可能尚未从根本上重塑经济，但人工智能领导者预计更大的变化即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-10/openai-coo-says-it-s-too-soon-to-see-ai-s-full-impact-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 20:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
